name: Nosey Skies
description:
Nosey McNostril, from Nosey Jumpers, is on another quest as a pilot flying through the skies of Noseville. Enjoy through multiple levels full of fun in this new installment of the Nosey Jumpers saga in augmented reality.

Version 1.0 of this app does not support the following:
-Saving game state through game sessions, such as your game score

Only available on devices that support ARKit (iOS 11 and above).

Thanks for your support!
